neutral.headline: Isabelle Tate, '9-1-1: Nashville' Star, Dies at Age 23
neutral.body_html: The world mourns as Isabelle Tate, a beloved star from the hit TV show '9-1-1: Nashville', passes away. Born on this day in [Year], she left us over the weekend at just 23 years old.

conservative.headline: '9-1-1: Nashville' Star Isabelle Tate Dies
conservative.body_html: Isabelle Tate, known for her role in the TV series '9-1-1: Nashville', has died. Born on this day [Year], she passed away over the weekend at 23 years old.

liberal.headline: Tragic Loss as Isabelle Tate, '9-1-1: Nashville' Star and Advocate for Mental Health Awareness Dies
liberal.body_html: Isabelle Tate was not only a star of the hit TV series '9-1-1: Nashville', but also an advocate who worked tirelessly to bring attention to mental health issues. Born on this day [Year], she tragically passed away over the weekend at just 23 years old.
